																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">22</div> <div class="vers-content">If men quarrel, and one strike a woman with child, and she miscarry indeed, but live herself: he shall be answerable for so much damage as the womanâ€™s husband shall require, and as arbiters shall award.</div></div></td>
